{
  "stem": "8753.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So she was an upper class, middle class.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So my mother approved of the friendship.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the other one's mother approved, as well, the--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not a tremendous, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We sort of lived where there we got along.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We got along.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not really.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father wore a regulator suit.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a little different.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, the peasants wore more, you know, plainer clothes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But my father used to wear a [NON-ENGLISH]-- do I have to explain it, [? a fore-hat-- ?] only on yontif, like kind of Rosh Hashanah in Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Saturday, I don't remember if he wore it on Saturday.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So as far as dressing, it was not outrageously different that my father dressed.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We tried to dress-- what was the difference?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was like, if somebody wore boots, so that was a sign of a [NON-ENGLISH], you know, a commoner.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I remember my mother never wore boots.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She wore those high shoes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was the style.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my father boots wintertime.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But summertimes, he always wore shoes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember my sister was friends with a boy in our village.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "His name was Leon Halpern, [NON-ENGLISH] they used to call him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were really in love.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "For a few years, they were going out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But he couldn't get married.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because he had an older sister, a single sister.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my father, especially, was on top of it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My-- my daughter, he said, you're wasting-- you're wasting your life away.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He's not going to get married, because his sister is not getting married.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So my father wanted to introduce my sister to a  boy.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he invited those two boys.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And two boys came that were friends or something.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they wore boots.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
